<item>
            <title>[SOLR-6685] ConcurrentModificationException in Overseer Stats API</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6685</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I just found a concurrent modification exception in OverseerCollectionProcessor while iterating over the overseer stats. The iteration should be synchronized.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12752021">SOLR-6685</key>
            <summary>ConcurrentModificationException in Overseer Stats API</summary>
